Package org.xlbean.converter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BeanConverter
    Converter for XlBean to generic class or vice-versa.
    ValueConverter
    Converter used for converting String values in XlBean to object or vice-versa.

    BeanConverterImpl
    Converter for XlBean to generic class or vice-versa.
    ValueConverterFactory  
    ValueConverterImpl
    Default implementation of ValueConverter.
